{"id": 2087, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X大宝】对你来说，“大宝”是一种怎样的存在？", "description": "最熟悉的人也有陌生的一面，最常见的护肤品也有隐藏功能。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 9089, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171228210437q4281CEvO3pMyxLg.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-29T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 257283, "content": "大宝涂脚丫子很滋润", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280111}, {"id": 257284, "content": "某年冬天，出门前我爸糊了我一脸大宝。然后，我就有了冬天擦大宝的习惯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093566}, {"id": 257286, "content": "钱多钱少呗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1044230}, {"id": 257287, "content": "妈妈的味道，擦上之后都被温柔包围了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795507}, {"id": 257288, "content": "刚在用，以前以为价格低是什么，结果真好用，干皮再也不怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725324}, {"id": 258568, "content": "上次没有带卸妆液，用了大宝居然可以卸妆！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225094}, {"id": 257289, "content": "不奢侈的精致品✌", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225543}, {"id": 257290, "content": "有情怀的存在", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 286987}, {"id": 258570, "content": "真的感觉有时候大宝滋润效果比某些大牌还好用！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225066}, {"id": 257291, "content": "据说成分和大牌一样？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 286987}, {"id": 257292, "content": "万能的吧，白天累了一天，洗完脸懒得再去拍水乳了，就直接挤点大宝，脸上一摸就好，有的时候也会当护手霜用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225547}, {"id": 258572, "content": "外国人都要加代购费买到的产品", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233694}, {"id": 257294, "content": "看了这么多评论，我发现居然只有我一个人对大宝过敏！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 