 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225731}, {"id": 257321, "content": "大宝卡\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784943}, {"id": 257323, "content": "大宝除了SOD密还有什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225746}, {"id": 257324, "content": "复古！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225749}, {"id": 257325, "content": "男同胞的护肤秘诀？\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 503421}, {"id": 257326, "content": "对我来说，这好似一条推广", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047562}, {"id": 257327, "content": "性价比之王啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176704}, {"id": 257328, "content": "随口就来：大宝SOD蜜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122421}, {"id": 257329, "content": "适合自己的才是最好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106579}, {"id": 257330, "content": "适合自己的才是最好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106579}, {"id": 257331, "content": "大宝天天见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151252}, {"id": 257332, "content": "适合老公用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156827}, {"id": 257333, "content": "爸爸的味道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950816}, {"id": 257589, "content": "于我冬天用着有点干，但看到办公室好多男同事在用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227875}, {"id": 257334, "content": "寒冷的保护器", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219205}, {"id": 257336, "content": "我还记得以前化学老师（女的）皮肤特别好，我们就问她怎么保养的，她说SOD的功效就是抗氧化，所以她只用大宝。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107204}, {"id": 257337, "content": "男生只要有大宝，一瓶走天下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "au